{"tid":2425439,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"下周兩會 北京封區檢測疑爆疫","createTime":"2021-02-27T10:43:38.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-27T10:43:38.000Z","uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"2c5c3fb431dffa0f6342d697145af8f9018fb888","tid":2425439,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-27T10:43:38.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/china/20210227/BHKIY646RVGUBM6O3KCVB3ODGA/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2F20210227%2FBHKIY646RVGUBM6O3KCVB3ODGA%2F&d=vb5EudyRk00tD8HubIiEmxOHaT3cO7pga%2FagQaCgUd0%3D&h=8d5bb6eb\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2F20210227%2FBHKIY646RVGUBM6O3KCVB3ODGA%2F&h=2560eb7b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/china/20210227/BHKIY646RVGUBM6O3KCVB3ODGA/</a><br />\n<br />\n下周兩會 北京封區檢測疑爆疫<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/ZXY-19PmNZhXxr5M1BU7n1wZq7A=/664x886/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/MCKJDL4WDNBXXPBFEXDCJE4IBE.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FZXY-19PmNZhXxr5M1BU7n1wZq7A%3D%2F664x886%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FMCKJDL4WDNBXXPBFEXDCJE4IBE.jpg&h=34ecb2a3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■北京兩會前夕，大興亦莊昨再封區檢疫。<br />\n<br />\n全國兩會即將於下周在京召開，當局嚴陣以待。不過北京日前卻有疫情傳出，當地有社區及工業園昨日臨時被封。有物管職員向內媒指，當局正在園內進行核酸檢測。<br />\n<br />\n涉事被封地點為北京大興亦莊的榮............................<br />\n<br />\n榮京麗都社區方面，有區內居民指：「..............................<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n須「14+7+7」隔離監測<br />\n<br />\n北京截至前日為止已連續27天沒有錄得本地確診病例，其間亦僅錄得零星外地輸入病例。為了確保全國兩會順利召開，北京近期為此採取最高規格的檢疫措施，當中包括對進京的人員採取「14+7+7」健康管理措施，即北京口岸入境人員在14天集中隔離期滿後，繼續七天居家或集中隔離，期滿後再進行七天健康監測。至於從中國其他口岸入境人員，則要隔離滿21天才可以進入北京，進京後尚須補足七天健康監測，未滿21天已進京的人員則須補足七天居家或集中隔離、七天健康監測。<br />\n<br />\n《北京日報》"}]}